      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "This was for QFN64 but some prices I got were :\nLow qty (~10) : 400 EUR setup + 150 EUR per piece\nLarger qty (>=100) : 4kEUR setup + 15 eur per piece.\n\nThat's a ballpartk of course. Might be a bit higher with more pins.",
